// JavaScript Code
// This Code will give us an error when it goes to production the error will be reference error that number is not defined 

function getTotal(numbers){
  number.reduce((acc, items)=>{
    return acc + items;
  },0)
}

getTotal([5,10,2030,58,40])


// In Typescript
// This Code will give us an error before goes to production the error will be reference error that number is not defined 
// Here we can tell this argumens to that this will be array of number 
function getTotal(numbers: Array<number>){  // this callecd generics
function getTotal(numbers: number[]){
  number.reduce((acc, items)=>{
    return acc + items;
  },0)
}

getTotal([5,10,2030,58,40])



First we have to compile typescript
to compile typescript to javascript run this command: tsc name of file that we have to compile it

typescript only for development when we compiled it the code of typecript are all gone and make like a vanilla js code
